name: Dade Murphy - Baby Hacker
description:
**SWITCH TO FULL SCREEN SO THE GAME DOESN'T JUMP AROUND**

Dade Murphy - Baby Hacker

Based (very loosely) on the classic film from when we were young Hackers

You are an elite baby hacker that must stop the bad guys from framing you!

A puzzle game in multi-game styles

Created for Game Jam 192 from Indie Game Squad
